creator: MonBuilding&Co
descriptionHtml:
Simple and secured, the Sharies app is the one-stop-shop while you stay with us. It gives you access to everything you need at your fingertips.

The app allows you to :
- Follow in real time what's going on in your Coliving space with news and incident reports.
- Communicate with Sharies members via messenger, forum and classified ads
- Benefit from services to make your daily life smoother: conciergerie, wellness and all other third party services integrated into the app
- Access your paiment information and your invoices.

The Sharies app is only available to members currently living at Sharies. If you are interested in becoming a member, visit us at https//sharies.co.

Sharies creates, operates and animates places made to Live & Meet, with the ambition of reinventing Housing by offering a full Experience that meets the needs and uses of today's urban people."
